
# Customer 360 Data Warehouse

## Business Problem

Customer data exists across multiple systems:

1. CRM System
2. Order Management System
3. Support System

Business users cannot get a single view of customers.

## Solution

Build a Customer 360 Data Warehouse using Azure Data Factory, Azure SQL Database, Azure Synapse Analytics and Power BI.

## Expected Outcomes

- Single customer view
- Customer revenue analysis
- Customer support analysis
- Executive reporting
